        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For lack of wood the fire goes out, and where there is no whisperer, quarreling ceases. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For lack of wood the fire goes out, and where there is no whisperer, quarreling ceases."
